query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS student_purchased_items (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  studentId INT NOT NULL,
  itemId INT NOT NULL,
  purchasedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  UNIQUE KEY unique_purchase (studentId, itemId)
)
